@host = http://localhost:5246

### 1. Create a Test Notification
POST {{host}}/api/Notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "title": "Bienvenido al sistema",
  "message": "Esta es una notificación de prueba para verificar la integración móvil.",
  "type": "General"
}

### 2. Get Notifications for Student 1
GET {{host}}/api/Notifications/student/1
Accept: application/json

### 3. Mark Notification as Read (Replace ID with one from previous step)
PUT {{host}}/api/Notifications/1/read

### 4. Create a Test Incident (Reporte)
POST {{host}}/api/Incidents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "title": "Reporte de conducta",
  "description": "El alumno mostró una actitud positiva en clase.",
  "typeId": 1,
  "reporterId": 1,
  "status": "Abierto"
}


### 6. Create Test Activities (Tasks Module)
